        "slowStartTime": 27324,
        "slowEndTime": 29326
    },
    {
        "text": "However, in phonology, it is the range of voice level available through the vocal cords.",
        "startTime": 20031,
        "endTime": 24946,
        "slowStartTime": 30196,
        "slowEndTime": 37644
    },
    {
        "text": "As language users, it is important for us to understand...",
